Package fr.univLille.cristal.shex.validation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Matcher
    Defines a custom condition on whether a neighbor triple matches a triple constraint.
    Typing
    A set of associations (resource, shape labels).
    ValidationAlgorithm
    Allows to validate a graph against a ShEx schema.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bag  
    BagIterator  
    DynamicCollectorOfTripleConstraint
    Recursively collects all triple constraints that appears in a shape.
    IntervalComputation
    Allows to compute the interval for a triple expression and a bag.
    MatcherPredicateAndValue
    Match the predicate and the value.
    MatcherPredicateOnly
    Match only the predicate.
    RecursiveTyping  
    RecursiveValidation
    Implements the Recursive validation algorithm.
    RefinementTyping
    The shape selected by default are the shapes of the set rules, the shapes that appear in a shape ref and the shapes that appear in a triple constraint.
    RefineValidation
    Implements the Refinement validation algorithm.
    SORBEGenerator
    Compute a SORBE version of a triple expression.
